statement.value:
CREATE ALGORITHM=UNDEFINED
DEFINER="root"@"localhost"
SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW `metadata_index_view` AS
SELECT
  `metadata_index`.`id` AS `id`,
  `metadata_index`.`urn` AS `urn`,
  `metadata_index`.`path` AS `path`,
  `metadata_index`.`doubleVal` AS `doubleVal`
FROM `metadata_index`
